dc_description_s: SARA Title III Hazardous Material locations (above ground). The dataset contains locations and attributes of Hazardous MaterialsC. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies. A dataset listing provided by DC FEMS identified above ground Hazardous Material locations.
